name: 2023 the 8th International Conference on Cloud Computing and Big Data Analytics
content: Publication: Submitted paper will be peer reviewed by conference committees, and accepted papers will be included in ICCCBDA 2023 Conference Proceedings, which will be archived in IEEE Xplore , and indexed by EI Compendex, Scopus, and other indexing services. http://icccbd.com/pub.html ICCCBDA 2023 is listed in IEEE conference calendar: https://conferences.ieee.org/conferences\_events/conferences/conferencedetails/56900
